#8 MICHELLE GUMABAO One of the most intimidating player to ever played in UAAP COURT. One wrong move on the net and she will make you pay. A textbook player & a leader. Mich became one of the most feared player in her time not only w/ her taunting but w/ that hands of steel!

#7 CAMILLE ABANTO When was the last time a 4-2 rotation in Ph Volleyball was used and became so effective? It was during her prime. Abanto/Semana Setter-Opp combination is one of the deadliest combo in UAAP history. Abanto is a great setter but an even greater Opp. All Hail!

#4 IRIS ORTEGA With the arrival of CRDJ in DLSU started an empire of future champions. And one of his first soldiers is Iris. Iris put DLSU on top of the mountain. She was CRDJ & DLSU's first MVP. She will always be the backbone of the now top Volleyball team, DLSU.

#3 JOAN BOTOR-CARPIO Before becoming country's God tier setter at that time. Joan is a natural opp hitter. She was nasty! She is a beast at the opposite position. She lead UST's glory and became UAAP 60 MVP! A beast Opp turned setter. No one is at her league during her time!

#2 AIZA MAIZO The Most Dominant Opposite Hitter Of All Time. The only PH player to have been recognized by Coach Lang Ping of China. The Most Aawarded Player in SVL. Her name will be remembered in the future generations as one of the GOATS of PH Volleyball.
